@startuml
title E Visa Processing and Follow-Up System State Diagram

[*] --> Initial

state Initial
state NotLoggedIn
state LoggedIn
state ApplicationSubmitted
state ApplicationProcessing
state ApplicationApproved
state ApplicationRejected
state LoggedOut

Initial --> NotLoggedIn : System starts

NotLoggedIn --> Initial : System reset

NotLoggedIn --> LoggedIn : User successfully logs in

LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User submits application after login
LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User submits application after login and payment

LoggedIn --> ApplicationProcessing : System processes application
LoggedIn --> ApplicationApproved : Application approved
LoggedIn --> ApplicationRejected : Application rejected

LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User modifies details
LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User views details
LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User gives feedback
LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User views purpose of application

ApplicationSubmitted --> ApplicationProcessing : Application is processed

ApplicationProcessing --> ApplicationApproved : Application approved
ApplicationProcessing --> ApplicationRejected : Application rejected

ApplicationApproved --> LoggedIn : User logs out
ApplicationRejected --> LoggedIn : User logs out

LoggedIn --> LoggedOut : User logs out after modifying details, viewing details, giving feedback, or completing status update

LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User views application status
LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User checks status

LoggedIn --> ApplicationSubmitted : User cancels application

